{"tid":1386493,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"728 衝突】據報警將控 45 人　涉暴動、襲擊等罪　明日提堂","createTime":"2019-07-30T11:00:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T11:28:53.000Z","uid":199434,"like":6,"dislike":40,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"0a923cea6ee1d60a1c5caa8ad169800fdc5cbadf","tid":1386493,"uid":199434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T11:00:06.000Z","msg":"反送中運動爆發多次嚴重警民衝突，星期日（7月28日）上環一帶警民衝突中，警方拘捕了 49 人，全部至今未獲准保釋，據報警方將落案檢控其中 45 人，控罪涉及暴動、襲擊、藏有攻擊性武器或阻差辦公等，<br />\n<br />\n《經濟日報》網站今午引述消息報道，45 人都會被控暴動罪，部分人同時會起訴阻差辦公、襲擊、藏有攻擊性武器等罪名，這批疑犯絕大部分是學生。<br />\n<br />\n《東方日報》也報道，據悉，警方將落案控告當中 45 人，包括一名機師，被控告人士涉及罪名包括暴動、襲擊、藏有攻擊性武器或阻差辦公，全部人明日（31日）東區法院提堂。<br />\n<br />\n另有知情人士向《立場新聞》表示，據悉大部份被捕都會被控非法集結。<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/728-%E8%A1%9D%E7%AA%81-%E6%93%9A%E5%A0%B1%E8%AD%A6%E5%B0%87%E6%8E%A7-45-%E4%BA%BA-%E6%B6%89%E6%9A%B4%E5%8B%95-%E8%A5%B2%E6%93%8A%E7%AD%89%E7%BD%AA-%E6%98%8E%E6%97%A5%E6%8F%90%E5%A0%82/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F728-%25E8%25A1%259D%25E7%25AA%2581-%25E6%2593%259A%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%25B0%2587%25E6%258E%25A7-45-%25E4%25BA%25BA-%25E6%25B6%2589%25E6%259A%25B4%25E5%258B%2595-%25E8%25A5%25B2%25E6%2593%258A%25E7%25AD%2589%25E7%25BD%25AA-%25E6%2598%258E%25E6%2597%25A5%25E6%258F%2590%25E5%25A0%2582%2F&d=R3EG5gZ7WKeJnJLyvNLCuZ2AEL7eB1GKmMTTK1c2%2F04%3D&h=aabaf83a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F728-%25E8%25A1%259D%25E7%25AA%2581-%25E6%2593%259A%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%25B0%2587%25E6%258E%25A7-45-%25E4%25BA%25BA-%25E6%25B6%2589%25E6%259A%25B4%25E5%258B%2595-%25E8%25A5%25B2%25E6%2593%258A%25E7%25AD%2589%25E7%25BD%25AA-%25E6%2598%258E%25E6%2597%25A5%25E6%258F%2590%25E5%25A0%2582%2F&h=1a5f08a5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/728-%E8%A1%9D%E7%AA%81-%E6%93%9A%E5%A0%B1%E8%AD%A6%E5%B0%87%E6%8E%A7-45-%E4%BA%BA-%E6%B6%89%E6%9A%B4%E5%8B%95-%E8%A5%B2%E6%93%8A%